videos.headline: Stevenson puts Houston on the board with 53-yard TD
videos.description: Clayton Tune throws to Clayton Stevenson, who breaks a tackle and eludes the rest of the Memphis defense for a 53-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Stevenson puts Houston on the board with 53-yard TD) 2019/11/16

videos.headline: White, Wilson connect for Memphis TD
videos.description: Brady White throws to an open Kameron Wilson for a six-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (White, Wilson connect for Memphis TD 2019/11/16

videos.headline: Tune takes it to the house for a 68-yard TD
videos.description: Houston QB Clayton Tune bursts up the middle and shakes off the defense en route to a 68-yard touchdown run.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tune takes it to the house for a 68-yard TD 2019/11/16

videos.headline: Coxie shakes off tackler for 23-yard TD
videos.description: Brady White dumps a pass off to Damonte Coxie, who loses his defender and finds the end zone for a 23-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Coxie shakes off tackler for 23-yard TD 2019/11/16

videos.headline: Austin leaps up to make nifty TD catch
videos.description: Calvin Austin III leaps up to haul in a nice 16-yard touchdown for Memphis off a throw from Brady White.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Austin leaps up to make nice TD catch 2019/11/16

videos.headline: Gibson goes airborne for a Memphis TD
videos.description: Antonio Gibson catches a short pass and takes to the air to get past the Houston defense for a six-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Gibson goes airborne for a Memphis TD 2019/11/16
